A cyberpunk cityscape at night viewed from above, showing glowing data streams flowing like neon rivers through a network of interconnected hexagonal container buildings. Each container structure pulses with different colored lights—cyan, magenta, and electric orange—representing different services. At the center, a massive angular gateway tower acts as the single entry point, funneling all the luminous data streams inward before distributing them to the smaller structures. The architecture features exposed mechanical pipes and circuit-board patterns etched into building surfaces. Rain slicks the streets below, reflecting the neon chaos above. Holographic traffic flows seamlessly through transparent tubes connecting the structures. The atmosphere is dense with fog and digital particles, creating depth and mystery in the sprawling techno-urban landscape.
